  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK606">
<l>paṭiyuṭaiyār paṟṟamaintakkaṇṇu maṭiyuṭaiyār </l>
<l> māṇpaya ṉeyta laritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is a rare thing for the idle, even when possessed of the riches of kings who ruled over the whole earth, to derive any great benefit from it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
